{"tid":47392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財爺行山變發哥 市民排長龍半小時為合照","createTime":"2016-12-20T10:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T13:49:26.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"210f330d10e9b2a2bc152bcad37a10389a16b926","tid":47392,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56070203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56070203&d=UEadKhIswHs4snaWK35HW3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=599b39ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56070203&h=7964d584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56070203</a><br />\n】<br />\n「如果癡癡的等 某日終於可等到&hellip;&hellip;」既然都要等，何不落區見見市民？已辭職9日但北京亦未批准的財政司司長曾俊華，今日facebook貼文自爆行山，而「攝影札記」專頁早前亦已上載相片顯示，有巿民行山時偶遇財爺曾俊華，排成一列長長的隊伍等候與財爺合照，情境猶如經常被「野生捕獲」的發哥周潤發，令山頂晨運徑出現一幕奇景。版主更形容隊伍「圍左差不多成半個鐘都未完」，又指當中部份人為瑪利諾學生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jW9AK3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjW9AK3h.jpg&h=9303a1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181555_02df2df5297e02556d6324d8799b4a90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181555_02df2df5297e02556d6324d8799b4a90.jpg&h=7b05ca79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8i181x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8i181x.jpg&h=d304fe4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/181556_07e89aac112b202bf3c0f80743dc5617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F181556_07e89aac112b202bf3c0f80743dc5617.jpg&h=38092